@startuml
' IOD(9)_Pj2_T-1 — User Story 9: Remove Uploaded File

skinparam DefaultFontName Arial
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #444444
skinparam ArrowColor #444444
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFFCC
skinparam NoteBorderColor #AAAAAA

title IOD(9)_Pj2_T-1\nUS9: Remove Uploaded File

start

:Actor navigates to the Uploaded Files Page;

:System displays list of all previously uploaded Excel files;

if (Any files in the list?) then (yes)

  :Actor selects the file to remove;

  :Actor clicks the "Remove" button next to the file;

  #ADD8E6:**ref** UC_REMOVE — Remove Uploaded File
  ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  System deletes the selected file from the uploads folder\nand removes its records from the schedule database;

  :System confirms successful removal;

  :Actor reviews updated file list\n(selected file is no longer present);

else (no)
  :System shows empty uploaded files list;
  :Actor has nothing to remove;
endif

stop
@enduml
